| Time | Phase | Activity | Description |
|------|-------|----------|-------------|
| 0-5 min | Connect | Math in Scratch | "How can we use the maths we learn in school in our projects?" |
| 5-12 min | Introduce | Green Operator Blocks | Demo: +, -, *, /, and where to find them. Show: Calculate score (base + bonus), random position |
| 12-20 min | Explore | Random Numbers | Random for: positions (random x, y), timing (random wait), values (random costume) |
| 20-32 min | Create | Maths Quiz Game | Start building: Generate random numbers, ask question, check answer |
| 32-40 min | Enhance | Difficulty Levels | Use operators to create harder levels (bigger numbers, time limits) |
| 40-45 min | Reflect | Operator Applications | "Where else could operators be useful?" |

